    <item>
      <title>拉马福萨计划设想南非成为建筑工地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-signals-faster-reforms-to-boost-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨表示，他的新多党政府将优先考虑经济增长，进行结构性改革，整顿管理不善的市政当局，减少繁文缛节，增加基础设施投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-signals-faster-reforms-to-boost-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>霍楚尔重申只要拜登继续竞选，他都会支持他</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ny-s-hochul-reaffirms-biden-support-as-long-as-he-stays-in-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州州长凯西·霍楚尔重申她对总统乔·拜登竞选的支持，并表示只要拜登继续寻求连任，她就会坚定不移地支持他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ny-s-hochul-reaffirms-biden-support-as-long-as-he-stays-in-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 17:48:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>突尼斯选举季开始，总统竞争对手被捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/tunisia-election-season-begins-with-president-s-rivals-arrested</link>
      <description><![CDATA[突尼斯选举季伊始，该国针对总统凯斯·赛义德的竞争对手和批评者展开了一系列逮捕行动，人们担心这场几乎没有竞争的选举结果将给这个曾经是阿拉伯世界最进步的民主国家造成沉重打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/tunisia-election-season-begins-with-president-s-rivals-arrested</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 16:22:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列考虑让欧盟和巴勒斯坦控制拉法口岸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/israel-considers-giving-control-of-gaza-s-rafah-crossing-to-eu-and-palestinians</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，以色列官员正在考虑将加沙拉法边境口岸的控制权移交给欧盟和巴勒斯坦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/israel-considers-giving-control-of-gaza-s-rafah-crossing-to-eu-and-palestinians</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:44:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登竞选团队坚称“没问题”，但退出压力越来越大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/biden-fine-campaign-insists-as-pressure-to-drop-out-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名顾问周四表示，总统乔·拜登在新冠病毒检测呈阳性后的第二天情况“良好”。但他的竞选活动却不太好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/biden-fine-campaign-insists-as-pressure-to-drop-out-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:38:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲领导人对特朗普在乌克兰问题上的温和立场持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/european-leaders-cast-wary-eye-to-trump-s-tepid-ukraine-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普第二任美国总统的前景，以及这对保卫乌克兰免受俄罗斯侵略意味着什么，悬在大西洋彼岸欧洲领导人重要会议上。]]></description>
